00:00:28.470 --> 00:00:30.032
Coconut Patties

00:00:36.954 --> 00:00:39.186
Ingredients required to cook Coconut Patties:

00:00:39.845 --> 00:00:42.975
Grated Coconut, Ginger garlic paste, Garam masala

00:00:43.415 --> 00:00:46.705
Rice Flour, Gram Flour, Corriander leaves, Salt

00:00:47.279 --> 00:00:52.328
Oil, Tomato sauce, Cashew nuts, Almonds, Onions, Chilli powder

00:01:02.474 --> 00:01:08.463
Firstly, take some grated coconut in a bowl

00:01:10.944 --> 00:01:14.393
Add a pinch of garam masala

00:01:17.963 --> 00:01:21.805
Add the required amount of salt

00:01:25.295 --> 00:01:28.422
Add 1/2 spoon full of ginger garlic paste

00:01:32.096 --> 00:01:48.224
Also add a spoon full of rice flour and gram flour as well
