00:01:57,583 --&gt; 00:01:37,893
Then, add some chilli powder and chopped onions

00:02:01.215 --> 00:02:09.038
Add some corriander leaves and mint leaves

00:02:13.618 --> 00:02:17.520
Meanwhile, heat some oil in the pan

00:02:21.181 --> 00:02:25.870
Mix the ingredients thoroughly and make a dough

00:02:27.333 --> 00:02:31.119
No need to add water in the dough

00:02:50.088 --> 00:02:59.843
Now, make patties with the dough and deep fry them

00:03:38.710 --> 00:03:46.416
Serve them in a plate with tomato sauce

